    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 23</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a blade of wind that cleaves through all enemies in the area, dealing 7d8 wind damage. The line cannot extend further than 100 ft.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 4 (up to 7d8+20 damage total).</p>\n\n",
